AI-OA Microservice Deployment Package
Version: 1.1.0
Release Date: 2026-05-01
Type: Non-Containerized Microservice Deployment (Bare Metal)
Branch: feature/kingbase-rabbitmq
Target: Medium-to-Large Enterprises (100-500 users)
Servers: 8-12 nodes
Components:
  - MySQL/MariaDB cluster (1 master + 1 slave)
  - Redis Cluster (3 nodes)
  - RabbitMQ Cluster (3 nodes)
  - MinIO Distributed (4 nodes)
  - Nginx + Keepalived load balancer
  - 13 Spring Boot microservices
  - Vue 3 frontend
